1.title: Jodie Whittaker, Pork Roast & Thai Curry

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: Jamie and Jimmy's end-of-the-pier cafe welcomes Doctor Who (2005) star Jodie Whittaker for a cooking lesson that is out of this world. They rustle up roast pork with crackling and an authentic Thai beef massaman curry.

2.title: Martin Freeman, Eggs Royale & Fish and Chips

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: Jamie and Jimmy welcome the actor for an unexpected journey in the cooking lesson of a lifetime. They crack the clues to a perfect eggs royale, a special take on fish and chips and a Japanese teppanyaki.

3.title: Danny DeVito, Korean Chicken & Back to School

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: The Hollywood star cooks a regional Italian dish with ingredients from the village where his grandparents lived. Jamie and Jimmy go back to school to campaign for a health rating scheme.

4.title: Harry Hill, Thali, Bangers & Steak

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Jamie and Jimmy take the comedian back to his days as a trainee doctor at the All India Institute in New Delhi by recreating the smells and tastes of aromatic thalis and parathas.

5.title: Romesh Ranganathan & Vegan Food

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: The chefs kick-off the new year with their first all-vegan menu. Romesh has been missing his favourite dish of lasagne since going vegan so they attempt a vegan version. Jimmy builds an apple press and they visit a vegan football stadium.

6.title: Jessica Ennis-Hill, Katsu Curry & Chocolate Fountain

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: Jamie and Jimmy are joined by Dame Jessica Ennis-Hill. On the menu is katsu curry and cod wrapped in Iberico ham. And Jimmy builds a chocolate fountain.

7.title: Stephen Fry & Apple Pie

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: Stephen Fry joins the chefs at their end-of-the-pier cafe. Recipes include apple pie the Essex way, sustainable seafood risotto, and veggie chilli.

8.title: Jessica Chastain, Cauliflower Tempura & Popcorn

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

8.plot: The menu goes vegan to recreate one of actress Jessica Chastain's favourite meals. Jimmy pimps up his popcorn. And the boys look into fortifying plant-based milks.

9.title: Burgers, Sir Patrick Stewart & Beer Grain

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

9.plot: Jamie and Jimmy bring back memories for Sir Patrick Stewart. Jamie makes a burger, Jimmy creates a rotating garden, and they discover how to reuse grain from brewing beer.

episode of.title: Jamie and Jimmy's Friday Night Feast (TV Series 2014– )

10.plot: Davina McCall joins the boys for some slow-cooked rabbit casserole. There's also spicy lamb, a beach BBQ, and a campaign to give teenagers a first taste of cooking.

plot: Jamie Oliver's got recipes to blow friends and family away. Jimmy Doherty shows how to cook great food you wouldn't usually try at home. Some very special guests drop by to help out in the kitchen and serve.::Mark_a_Wood <markawood@hotmail.co.uk>
